title: Community Nature Walk
description_html: Join us for a refreshing morning walk through the beautiful Riverside Park. A great way to connect with nature and neighbors.

title: Seniors Tech Support Drop-in
description_html: Having trouble with your smartphone, tablet, or computer? Our volunteers are here to help! Drop in anytime during the session for one-on-one assistance.

title: Annual Summer Bingo Bash
description_html: Get your dabbers ready for our Annual Summer Bingo Bash! Great prizes and a fun evening guaranteed. Price includes one bingo card.

title: Healthy Eating Workshop
description_html: Learn to cook delicious and nutritious meals on a budget. This interactive workshop includes live demonstrations and recipe handouts to take home.

title: Chair Yoga Session
description_html: A gentle yoga session suitable for all mobility levels. Improve flexibility, balance, and relaxation from the comfort of a chair. No experience necessary.

title: Rural Transportation Town Hall
description_html: Have your voice heard on the future of transportation in our community. Local officials will be present to answer questions and discuss upcoming projects.

title: Gardening Club Meetup
description_html: Share tips, swap seeds, and enjoy a pleasant afternoon with fellow gardening enthusiasts. All are welcome, from beginners to seasoned experts.

title: Introduction to Digital Banking
description_html:
Learn the basics of online and mobile banking in a safe and supportive environment. This session will cover:

  • Logging in safely
  • Checking balances
  • Paying bills online

title: Fall Flu Shot Clinic
description_html: Protect yourself and your community this flu season. Free flu shots are available on a walk-in basis. Please bring your health card.

title: Winter Holiday Gala
description_html: Celebrate the holiday season with an elegant evening of dinner, dancing, and live music. A perfect way to connect with friends and neighbors. Formal attire is encouraged.
